                     <interp inst="t17840915-56-defend699" type="age" value="thirteen"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             (aged thirteen) was indicted for <rs id="t17840915-56-off277" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17840915-56-off277" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840915-56-off277" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17840915-56-cd278" type="crimeDate">10th day of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840915-56-off277 t17840915-56-cd278"></join>, one leather purse, value 1 d. forty-two guineas, value 44 l. 2 s. one half guinea, value 10 s. 6 d. two crown pieces, value 10 s. six half crown pieces, value 15 s. and six shillings and sixpence in monies numbered, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17840915-56-victim701" type="victimName">
                           Simon 
                           Shepherd
                        <interp inst="t17840915-56-victim701" type="surname" value="Shepherd"></interp>
